metadata.name: Akash
metadata.description:
Speak not of Her, child,
for She is everywhere and nowhere:
Chaos, the Mother,
the Unmanifest Space.
She witnesses onâ€”
with her smile, sweet as death:
your wounds, your words,
your deeds, your desires,
your path, your perversion,
your monsters,
and your madness.

She longs to taste
every
single
morsel
of it.

Where could you run, child,
when her womb alone
sustains
all worlds?
